By: Thomas Traherne
---
To be satisfied in God is the highest difficulty in the whole world, and yet
most easy ... because God is. For God is not a being compounded of body and
soul, or substance and accident, or power and act, but is all act, pure act,
a Simple Being whose essence is to be, whose Being is to be perfect.
